Title: It's A Wonderful Lie
Plot: A mother's sudden paralysis during a indoor rock-climbing incident leaves her daughter injured, and House's new team looking for a cure. Meanwhile, House organizes his new recruits' Secret Santa gift exchange... with a few twists of his own.
GuestStars: Janel Moloney, Liana Liberato, Cheyenne Wilbur, Scotty Maguire, Jennifer Hall, Anthony Starke
